<view class="page index-page">
  <view class="hero card">
    <view class="brand-line">
      <view class="brand-mark">G</view>
      <view>
        <text class="brand-name">GeoGi 几何智引</text>
        <text class="brand-sub">AI 时代的品牌可见度增长系统</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <text class="eyebrow">AI VISIBILITY SYSTEM</text>
    <text class="h1">让品牌在 AI 时代被看见、被理解、被选择</text>
    <text class="lead">GeoGi 帮助企业诊断并提升在 AI 问答、智能搜索和生成式推荐场景中的品牌呈现质量。</text>

    <view class="actions">
      <button class="primary-button" bindtap="goDiagnosis">开始品牌诊断</button>
      <button class="secondary-button" bindtap="goServices">查看服务</button>
    </view>

    <view class="signal-panel">
      <view class="signal-orbit">
        <view class="signal-core">
          <text>GeoGi</text>
          <text>AI Visibility</text>
        </view>
        <view class="signal-chip chip-a">品牌</view>
        <view class="signal-chip chip-b">内容</view>
        <view class="signal-chip chip-c">信源</view>
      </view>
      <view class="signal-list">
        <view class="signal-item" wx:for="{{signals}}" wx:key="*this">
          <view class="dot"></view>
          <text>{{item}}</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section pain-card card">
    <text class="eyebrow">WHY GEO</text>
    <text class="h2">当用户问 AI 时，AI 会推荐你吗？</text>
    <view class="pain-list">
      <view class="pain-item" wx:for="{{pains}}" wx:key="*this">
        <view class="dot"></view>
        <text>{{item}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-head">
      <text class="eyebrow">CAPABILITY</text>
      <text class="h2">核心检测能力</text>
      <text class="body">不只看“有没有出现”，还会看是否被正确理解、是否被主动推荐，以及答案背后的信源是否可靠。</text>
    </view>
    <view class="ability-grid">
      <view class="ability-card card" wx:for="{{abilities}}" wx:key="*this">{{item}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section stats-row">
    <view class="metric card" wx:for="{{metrics}}" wx:key="label">
      <text class="metric-value">{{item.value}}</text>
      <text class="metric-label">{{item.label}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-head">
      <text class="eyebrow">SERVICES</text>
      <text class="h2">从诊断到持续优化</text>
      <text class="body">首版小程序聚焦咨询转化与专业信任建设，后续可继续加入报告查询、客户案例和内容订阅。</text>
    </view>
    <view class="list">
      <view class="service-card card" wx:for="{{services}}" wx:key="title">
        <text class="pill">{{item.tag}}</text>
        <text class="card-title">{{item.title}}</text>
        <text class="body">{{item.desc}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section flow-card card">
    <text class="eyebrow">PROCESS</text>
    <text class="h2">服务流程清楚可预期</text>
    <view class="flow-list">
      <view class="flow-item" wx:for="{{flow}}" wx:key="*this">
        <text class="flow-num">0{{index + 1}}</text>
        <text class="flow-title">{{item}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section report-card card">
    <view>
      <text class="eyebrow">SAMPLE REPORT</text>
      <text class="h2">先看报告长什么样</text>
      <text class="body">示例报告展示检测维度、证据截图、平台表现和优化路线，正式客户报告会做脱敏和人工复核。</text>
    </view>
    <button class="secondary-button report-button" bindtap="goReport">查看示例报告</button>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-head">
      <text class="eyebrow">RESEARCH</text>
      <text class="h2">GeoGi 研究中心</text>
    </view>
    <view class="list">
      <view class="article-card card" wx:for="{{latestArticles}}" wx:key="id" data-id="{{item.id}}" bindtap="openArticle">
        <text class="pill">{{item.category}}</text>
        <text class="card-title">{{item.title}}</text>
        <text class="body">{{item.desc}}</text>
        <text class="article-date">{{item.date}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section faq-card card">
    <text class="eyebrow">FAQ</text>
    <text class="h2">常见问题</text>
    <view class="faq-item" wx:for="{{faqs}}" wx:key="q">
      <text class="faq-q">{{item.q}}</text>
      <text class="body">{{item.a}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section cta-card">
    <text class="cta-title">先判断品牌是否已经进入 AI 答案</text>
    <text class="cta-copy">用一次轻量诊断，找到当前最值得补强的品牌内容和信源缺口。</text>
    <button class="primary-button cta-button" bindtap="goDiagnosis">开始品牌诊断</button>
    <button class="text-link" bindtap="goResearch">查看研究方法</button>
  </view>

  <button class="sticky-cta" bindtap="goContact">联系顾问</button>
  <view class="safe-bottom"></view>
</view>
